tool_description: When provided with a URL containing an image of a vehicle, this API will return the details of the license plate as seen in in the image
name: License plate from Image
title: License plate from Image

api_list.name: PlateRecognizerLambda
api_list.description:
In this endpoint you supply a JSON body in the following form
{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WPXs6vNiSb4/maxresdefault.jpg"}
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://license-plate-from-image.p.rapidapi.com/PlateRecognizerLambda"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "license-plate-from-image.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
